works.description: First shown in late 2010, the 7-Series Steinway & Sons Limited Edition has been now introduced in China. Created by BMW Individual as part of an exclusive partnership with New York-based piano manufacturer Steinway & Sons, the special edition 7er was launched at a special event in China. The 7-Series Steinway & Sons will be available in China in two versions - the V8-powered 740i and the flagship 760i with a 544HP twin-turbocharged V12 - priced at 1,798,000 Yuan ($275,000) and 3,198,000 Yuan ($489,260) respectively.
